sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Edge Device
    participant E as Edge Management System
    participant O as System Operator
    participant A as Application Publisher
    participant C as Application Certifier<br/>(Optional)

    Note over O,E: Application deployment
    O->>E: Deploy application and manifest
    E->>D: Transfer application and manifest
    D->>D: Verify application image hash
    D->>D: Verify operator authorization
    D->>D: Verify local trust requirements
    D->>D: Install application

